/info /* Info about project */
    MySqlSettings  /* Settings for MySql (/etc/mysql/my.cnf) */

--------------------------------------------------------------------
   
1) Edit '/etc/mysql/my.cnf' file.
2) Create database 'tnews' (in MySql).
3) Set your 'USER', 'PASSWORD' in 'settings.py'.
4) python manage.py sqlall tnews
5) python manage.py syncdb   - to create tables in database.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
python manage.py runserver
Go to 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/filldb' (for fill your database).
Go to 'http://127.0.0.1:8000' !



--------------------------------------------------------------------
What's new?

- scrolling tweets with the mouse wheel
- load tweets from database
